g.text: I HAVE PRINTED THE RULES AND REGULATIONS
FOLD OR CUT ALONG DOTTED LINE AND DISPLAY IN FRONT WINDSHIELD

PLEASE FILL OUT THE MONTH AND DAY YOU PLAN TO CUT YOUR TREE DOWN
